    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将扩大小企业税收减免以促进初创企业发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/harris-to-expand-small-business-tax-relief-to-boost-startups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯提议将小企业启动成本的税收减免提高十倍，这是她与唐纳德·特朗普竞争以向选民表明谁最能缓解他们对经济的担忧时使用的新武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/harris-to-expand-small-business-tax-relief-to-boost-startups</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:00:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国移民法庭不注重正义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/us-immigration-court-system-falls-to-politics-failing-asylum-seekers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[决定庇护案件的系统正在失败，这不仅仅是因为它不堪重负。必须采取一些大胆的措施来修复一个从本质上就有缺陷的程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-03/us-immigration-court-system-falls-to-politics-failing-asylum-seekers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普转变立场，支持大麻合法化（前提是正确实施）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-in-shift-backs-marijuana-legalization-if-done-correctly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示支持其家乡佛罗里达州的大麻合法化，该州选民已经在投票中表决允许娱乐性使用大麻，这标志着这位前总统的政策发生重大转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-in-shift-backs-marijuana-legalization-if-done-correctly</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 20:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州和地方养老金支付将增加 9 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/new-york-state-and-local-pension-payments-to-rise-900-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在福利优惠措施获得州议员批准且公务员工资上涨后，纽约州及其纽约市以外的地方政府将在下一财年向州养老金基金额外缴纳 9 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/new-york-state-and-local-pension-payments-to-rise-900-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 20:37:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
